com.cognos.CAM_AAA.authentication

Class TextNoEchoDisplayObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cognos.CAM_AAA.authentication.TextDisplayObject
      • com.cognos.CAM_AAA.authentication.TextNoEchoDisplayObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDisplayObject, ITextDisplayObject, ITextNoEchoDisplayObject

    public class TextNoEchoDisplayObject
extends TextDisplayObject
implements ITextNoEchoDisplayObject
    A display object that allows the user to type in information. The information typed is not echoed for the user to see. Instead, asterisks (*) are echoed.
